{"id":376674,"date":[{"year":1958,"month":9,"day":15}],"page":"6","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"427","ytitle":"","mtitle":"人民公社好","ftitle":"人民公社十大优越性图画唱本","authors":[],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>中共商城县委宣传部编</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入4号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1958\\09\\589f060101.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>总路线放光芒，遍地鲜花齐开放，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民公社已建成，万众一心齐欢唱。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入4号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1958\\09\\589f060102.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>共产党领导真英明，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民公社有十大优越性，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第一能巩固集体主义所有制，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能培养集体主义的精神。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入4号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1958\\09\\589f060103.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>第二能进一步发展工农业，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能实现工农业并举的方针，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到处机器轰隆隆的响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"商城面貌日日新。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入4号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1958\\09\\589f060104.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>第三加速农业机械化，笨犁笨耙全革新，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"耕田用上小铁牛，人人乐得笑盈盈。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入4号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1958\\09\\589f060105.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>第四便于进行大型建设，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有力向自然大进军，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水利机械自流化，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工厂矿山遍布全商城。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入4号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1958\\09\\589f060106.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>第五社大人多资源广，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"便于发展多种经济，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穷山变为金银山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"荒地变为聚宝盆。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入4号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1958\\09\\589f060107.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>第六社大领导骨干强，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"统一调配劳力更便当，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"培养大量红专队伍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"调动一切积极力量。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入4号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1958\\09\\589f060108.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>第七社社队队办大学，脑力体力无界线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"培养大量建设人材，各种专家样样全。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入4号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1958\\09\\589f060109.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>第八民校剧团村村有，社里建立幸福院，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东西南北有公路，交通运输多方便。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入4号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1958\\09\\589f060110.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>第九人民公社力量强，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"消灭灾害有力量，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不怕一年不下雨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亩产万斤有保障。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入4号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1958\\09\\589f060111.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>第十党的领导能加强，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社组织坚如钢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远跟着毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远跟着共产党。</FONT>"}]}